{"tid":1276753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 元州邨2小時內先後2名男子墮樓身亡","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T05:05:29.000Z","uid":17607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e6f757aa7f86c86ed849e6bc8cf7cda253e368","tid":1276753,"uid":17607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】本港連日發生多宗墮樓案件，深水埗元州邨約2個小時內先後有2名男子墮樓身亡，警方未有檢獲遺書，但認為事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。警方正了解兩人墮樓自殺原因。<br />\n<br />\n早上9時，一名49歲姓曾男子被發現倒臥元雅樓外昏迷，警方及救護員接報到場，將男子送明愛醫院搶救，證實不治。警方初步調查，相信死者從單位墮下，正尋找其親友了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早上11時，一名94歲姓鄧老翁亦由高處墮下，倒臥元禧樓對開，救護員到場證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%83%E5%B7%9E%E9%82%A82%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%85%A7%E5%85%88%E5%BE%8C2%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1-074400946.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%2582%25A82%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%25BE%258C2%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BA%25A1-074400946.html&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=ca731233\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%83%E5%B7%9E%E9%82%A82%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%85%A7%E5%85%88%E5%BE%8C2%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1-074400946.html</a>"},{"pid":"896f40dd6e561804c4072e0465570c9980de07a9","tid":1276753,"uid":149653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"「警方<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未有撿獲遺書</span></span>」極有可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cb33589b8e4037d9bd2406ff8ad00b4f65f9da","tid":1276753,"uid":180462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"896f40dd6e561804c4072e0465570c9980de07a9","tid":1276753,"uid":149653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T0